name: BlkdPovBJ (Beta)
description:
Disclaimer: Use ethically/responsibly ! By downloading you agree to bear full responsibility of the images/models produced from this.

Blacked POV Blowjob model, created via finetuning sd 1.5 with captions. No instance token or class, so the model is quite flexible and was trained with natural english custom prompts. Mostly works with POV shots as the training data had mostly those, but side shots can work if using img2img.

Works extremely well with img2img, but not required.

Note: Use the stable diffusion 1.5 VAE for best results.


Recommended Settings:

Example prompt:

An exquisite photograph of a gorgeous sexy blonde woman with beautiful eyes, sucking a huge thick black cock.

To specify facial expression add at the end: (sad/angry/happy look on her face) and/or (eyes closed)

To specify background add at the end (as examples): fireplace in the background /fancy sea resort in the background/in a living room/sitting on a wooden floor

You can also specify jewlery, add for example "with hoop earrings" right after you describe the woman.

Negative Prompt: Ugly,deformed,disfigured,extra limbs,extra digits,3d render,videogame,doll,plastic,wrinkles,old

Sampler: Euler A or dpm++ 2M Karras

Steps: 36-60

CFG: 8-8.5
